title: Converse Rubber Tracks: Studio Tour
description:
Take an inside peek into Converse Rubber Tracks. The talented Albert Hammond, Jr. takes you on a behind-the-scenes studio tour.

Converse Rubber Tracks is a community-based professional recording studio in Brooklyn, NY. Emerging musicians of all genres can apply for free studio time at Converse.com/rubbertracks. If selected, artists record for free while maintaing the rights to their own music. 

To learn more about Converse Rubber Tracks and to apply for studio time go to http://www.converse.com/rubbertracks.
